{"id": "1248282679615688875", "channel_id": "1248282679615688875", "type": 0, "author_id": "1223503015852380160", "author_name": "squire5771", "author_bot": false, "content": "H2-6，H7-6，H7-9对应的普通难度有隐藏银芯，但是这些关我重试了一下还是没有发现有隐藏银芯，倒也不是很在意那一点，只是作为强迫症有点难受，希望校工能反馈一下问题。", "timestamp": "2024-06-06T14:29:42.791000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [{"emoji": "bow", "emoji_id": "1243504932460433498", "count": 2}], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1248282679615688875", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "关于困难主线某些关没有隐藏银芯的问题", "forum_channel_id": "1180845276823564288", "is_thread_starter": true, "thread_tags": ["1181168197425172480"]}
